---
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import { wedding } from '../data/wedding';
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="Travel & Lodging">
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Travel & Lodging"
    title="Transportation, lodging, and travel notes."
    description="We're so excited to celebrate our marriage with you! Here you'll find information about getting to Estes Park, lodging recommendations, and other tips to make your trip as easy as possible."
  />

  <section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="section-shell flex flex-col gap-10">
      <div class="rounded-md bg-linen p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
        <p class="eyebrow">Getting here</p>
        <h2 class="section-h2">Denver International Airport</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/75">
          DIA is the closest major airport, about 1.5 hours away from Estes Park. You can rent a car or book a shuttle
          to take you to Estes Park. Estes Park Shuttle is the only shuttle service we currently know of. Check back soon
          for our Estes Park Shuttle 10% discount code.
        </p>
      </div>

<div class="rounded-md bg-mist p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
  <p class="eyebrow">Lodging</p>
  <h2 class="section-h2">Our recommendations</h2>

  <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-ink/75">
  We will not have a hotel block. We recommend staying at the YMCA not only for its proximity to our venue, but for the beautiful location surrounded by the National Park and the many fun activities offered. However, if staying at the Y is not your preference, some good options in Estes Park include the iconic Stanley Hotel or the Trailhead Lodge. NW Longmont and Lyons have additional, sometimes more affordable options, but are about 45 minutes to 1 hour away from our venue by car.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4">

 <div class="grid gap-6">
  <!-- Cabins -->
  <a
    href="https://www.ymcarockies.org/stay/cabins"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="relative rounded-md border border-ink/10 bg-white p-4 transition hover:border-forest hover:shadow-soft"
  >
    <span class="absolute right-4 top-4 rounded-full bg-forest px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white">
      ❤️ Our Pick
    </span>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">
      YMCA Cabins <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </h3>

    <p class="mt-1 text-ink/75">
      Private cabins of different sizes for families and groups, with full kitchens, fireplaces, and mountain views. IMPORTANT: Make sure to book under "Estes Park Center Cabins".
    </p>

    <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-forest">
      🚗 5-minute shuttle ride to the wedding venue!
    </p>
  </a>

  <!-- Lodge -->
  <a
    href="https://www.ymcarockies.org/stay/lodge-rooms"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="relative rounded-md border border-ink/10 bg-white p-4 transition hover:border-forest hover:shadow-soft"
  >
     <span class="absolute right-4 top-4 rounded-full bg-forest px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white">
      ❤️ Our Pick
    </span>
    
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">
      YMCA Lodge Rooms <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </h3>

    <p class="mt-1 text-ink/75">
      Hotel-style rooms that are perfect for couples or guests looking for a simpler, affordable stay. See below for the quiet, convenient lodges recommended by the Y's wedding coordinator. IMPORTANT: Make sure to book under "Estes Park Center".
    </p>
    
    <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside text-ink/75 space-y-1">
  <li>Wind River Lodge</li>
  <li>Aspen Lodge</li>
  <li>Alpen Inn Lodge</li>
  <li>Emerald Mountain Lodge</li>
  <li>Longs Peak Lodge</li>
  <li>Rams Horn Lodge</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-forest">
      🚗 5-minute shuttle ride to the wedding venue!
    </p>
  </a>
</div>

    <a
  href="https://www.stanleyhotel.com/"
  target="_blank"
  rel="noopener noreferrer"
  class="rounded-md border border-ink/10 bg-white p-4 transition hover:border-forest hover:shadow-soft"
>
  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">
    The Stanley Hotel <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
  </h3>

  <p class="mt-1 text-ink/75">
    The elegant and absolutely iconic hotel that inspired <em>The Shining</em>. A spa and nice restaurants. The most upscale option, but not too expensive. Probably not haunted.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-forest">
    🚗 16-minute drive to the Y parking lot, plus 5-min shuttle ride
  </p>
</a>

    <a
  href="https://trailheadlodgeestes.com/"
  target="_blank"
  rel="noopener noreferrer"
  class="rounded-md border border-ink/10 bg-white p-4 transition hover:border-forest hover:shadow-soft"
>
  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">
    Trailhead Lodge <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
  </h3>

  <p class="mt-1 text-ink/75">
    Lodge with nice rooms and suites in the heart of Estes Park. Pet friendly with fun amenities. In between the Y and the Stanley in terms of affordability.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-medium text-forest">
    🚗 15-minute drive to the Y parking lot, plus 5-min shuttle ride
  </p>
</a>

  </div>
</div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-linen py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="section-shell grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Airport</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.airport}</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Parking</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.parking}</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Transportation</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.transportation}</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-md bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="section-h2">Elevation</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-ink/75">{wedding.travel.elevation}</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
